tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE training_data (
  sample_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  gene_id INT,
  label VARCHAR(50),
  data BLOB,
  FOREIGN KEY (gene_id) REFERENCES gene_expression_data(gene_id)
);

CREATE TABLE gene_experiments (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    gene_id INT,
    experiment_date DATE NOT NULL,
    experimental_condition VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (gene_id) REFERENCES gene_sequences(gene_id)
);

CREATE TABLE model_training_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT,
    input_data TEXT NOT NULL,
    output_data TEXT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES gene_experiments(experiment_id)
);
